1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Mchezo wa Kwanza: Maoni kuhusu Mchezo wa Japan dhidi ya Brazil

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:07,590
Uliuona mchezo wa mpira wa jana?

3
00:00:07,614 --> 00:00:11,391
Ndio, niliuona.

4
00:00:11,414 --> 00:00:15,514
Mchezo wa Japan na Brazil, ndio?

5
00:00:15,537 --> 00:00:18,171
Ndio.

6
00:00:18,194 --> 00:00:23,627
Japan ilishindwa 1-2.

7
00:00:23,650 --> 00:00:27,750
Kweli ni jambo la kusikitisha.

8
00:00:27,773 --> 00:00:32,906
Lakini hadi mwisho ulikuwa mchezo mzuri.

9
00:00:32,929 --> 00:00:35,398
Eeh.

10
00:00:35,422 --> 00:00:40,960
Goli la Japan katika kipindi cha kwanza lilikuwa zuri sana.

11
00:00:40,984 --> 00:00:44,569
Mimi pia nilifurahishwa sana.

12
00:00:44,592 --> 00:00:49,325
Ulinzi wa Japan ulikuwa bora pia.

13
00:00:49,348 --> 00:00:51,946
Ndiyo, kweli.

14
00:00:51,969 --> 00:00:58,368
Walizuia mashambulizi makali ya Brazil mara kadhaa.

15
00:00:58,391 --> 00:01:05,172
Hata asubuhi, Brazil iliongeza nguvu zaidi baada ya mapumziko.

16
00:01:05,196 --> 00:01:07,465
Ndio.

17
00:01:07,488 --> 00:01:14,257
Katika kipindi cha pili, Brazil walikuwa na pasi za haraka sana.

18
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:19,783
Goli la mwisho lilikuwa shuti kali sana.

19
00:01:19,807 --> 00:01:25,274
Kama ilivyokuwa, timu ya kwanza duniani kwa daraja.

20
00:01:25,297 --> 00:01:29,217
Walikuwa wazito mno.

21
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:36,473
Ingawa ni hasira, niligundua machozi ya wachezaji wa Japan.

22
00:01:36,496 --> 00:01:42,432
Mimi pia nilipiga makofi mbele ya televisheni.

23
00:01:42,456 --> 00:01:50,245
Wapo katika robo fainali, lakini hakuna sababu ya kusikitika.

24
00:01:50,268 --> 00:01:52,706
Eeh.

25
00:01:52,730 --> 00:01:59,209
Wameonyesha kuwa wanaweza kukabiliana na timu kubwa.

26
00:01:59,232 --> 00:02:05,782
Natumai kuona Japan yenye nguvu zaidi katika Kombe la Dunia baada ya miaka minne.

27
00:02:05,805 --> 00:02:07,987
Ndio.

28
00:02:08,010 --> 00:02:14,044
Kwa hakika, tutaona timu bora zaidi ya Japan.

29
00:02:14,067 --> 00:02:20,567
Hadi wakati huo, tuendelee kuwashabikia.

30
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:23,023
Ndiyo, kweli.

31
00:02:23,046 --> 00:02:29,154
Leo tutakula chakula kitamu ili kupata nguvu.

32
00:02:29,178 --> 00:02:31,711
Sawa kabisa.

33
00:02:31,734 --> 00:02:36,034
Je, twende kula nyama ya kuchoma?

34
00:02:36,057 --> 00:02:39,057
Mchezo wa Pili: Kutabiri Fainali ya Kombe la Dunia

35
00:02:39,057 --> 00:02:45,235
Kombe la Dunia la soka limekaribia mwisho.

36
00:02:45,259 --> 00:02:52,767
Ndio. Timu zilizosalia zote ni timu kubwa.

37
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:59,724
Kwa hakika, unafikiri fainali itakuwa kati ya timu gani mwaka huu?

38
00:02:59,747 --> 00:03:06,546
Ninafikiri itakuwa mchezo kati ya Brazil na Ufaransa.

39
00:03:06,569 --> 00:03:10,836
Mchezo wa kawaida.

40
00:03:10,859 --> 00:03:14,759
Kwa nini timu hizi mbili?

41
00:03:14,782 --> 00:03:21,661
Brazil ina nguvu zaidi katika mashindano haya.

42
00:03:21,685 --> 00:03:25,399
Kweli, ni hivyo.

43
00:03:25,422 --> 00:03:31,127
Mshambuliaji Neymar ana nguvu kubwa.

44
00:03:31,151 --> 00:03:36,984
Ufaransa ina ulinzi imara sana.

45
00:03:37,007 --> 00:03:41,641
Wana uzoefu wa mabingwa wa zamani.

46
00:03:41,664 --> 00:03:45,565
Mchezaji Mbappé pia ni mwepesi.

47
00:03:45,588 --> 00:03:52,294
Ndio. Kwa hiyo, timu hizi mbili zitafika fainali.

48
00:03:52,318 --> 00:03:56,757
Unadhani ni timu gani itashinda?

49
00:03:56,780 --> 00:03:59,962
Tafadhali, jaribu kutabiri kwa ujasiri.

50
00:03:59,985 --> 00:04:06,092
Nitaweka pesa yangu kwa Brazil kuwa mabingwa.

51
00:04:06,115 --> 00:04:11,415
Je, ni kwa sababu ya ustadi wa mtu binafsi?

52
00:04:11,438 --> 00:04:14,105
Ndio.

53
00:04:14,128 --> 00:04:21,761
Mtindo wa kucheza wa Amerika Kusini utavunja utaratibu wa Ulaya.

54
00:04:21,784 --> 00:04:26,818
Sawa. Uchambuzi mzuri sana.

55
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:30,974
Nadhani ni Ufaransa.

56
00:04:30,997 --> 00:04:34,706
Ufaransa tena mabingwa?

57
00:04:34,729 --> 00:04:37,863
Sababu ni nini?

58
00:04:37,886 --> 00:04:43,753
Timu yao ina wachezaji wengi wenye uwezo, mtu yeyote aingie na anaweza kuwa hodari.

59
00:04:43,776 --> 00:04:47,850
Wana mikakati mingi sana.

60
00:04:47,873 --> 00:04:54,552
Hakika, hata kama watapata majeraha, nguvu ya timu haipungui.

61
00:04:54,575 --> 00:05:00,475
Fainali itakuwa mapambano ya kihistoria.

62
00:05:00,498 --> 00:05:04,965
Ni vigumu kusema ni nani atakayeibuka mshindi.

63
00:05:04,988 --> 00:05:08,555
Ninategemea sana tayari!

64
00:05:08,578 --> 00:05:11,578
Sehemu ya 3: Uvutio wa Kuangalia Sumo Moja kwa Moja

65
00:05:11,578 --> 00:05:18,286
Je, tutaenda kuangalia sumo wikendi ijayo?

66
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:21,076
Sumo?

67
00:05:21,099 --> 00:05:26,533
Sijawahi kuona hata mara moja.

68
00:05:26,556 --> 00:05:29,456
Tunapaswa kwenda!

69
00:05:29,479 --> 00:05:33,712
Mahali ni Kokugikan (Ukumbi wa Kitaifa wa Sumo).

70
00:05:33,735 --> 00:05:39,888
Ninawaona kwenye televisheni, lakini je, ukweli una nguvu zaidi?

71
00:05:39,911 --> 00:05:44,544
Ndiyo, tofauti ni kubwa kabisa!

72
00:05:44,567 --> 00:05:49,667
Mabingwa wa sumo wana miili kubwa sana.

73
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:54,824
Je, sauti ya miili ikipigana inasikika hadi kwenye viti?

74
00:05:54,847 --> 00:06:02,381
Ndiyo. Sauti ya 'pachin!' inasikika kote ukumbini.

75
00:06:02,404 --> 00:06:06,104
Hiyo inaonekana ya kuvutia!

76
00:06:06,127 --> 00:06:10,198
Je, tiketi zipo bado?

77
00:06:10,222 --> 00:06:15,922
Kwenye ghorofa ya pili, viti vya mbao bado vinaweza kukubaliwa.

78
00:06:15,945 --> 00:06:18,703
Sawa sana!

79
00:06:18,726 --> 00:06:24,400
Je, naweza kula chakula cha mkeka ndani ya Kokugikan?

80
00:06:24,424 --> 00:06:28,158
Ndiyo, hakuna shida.

81
00:06:28,181 --> 00:06:33,314
Kuku wa kuchoma ni maarufu sana na ni tamu mno!

82
00:06:33,337 --> 00:06:37,729
Kuku wa kuchoma katika ukumbi wa sumo?

83
00:06:37,752 --> 00:06:40,486
Ni ajabu!

84
00:06:40,509 --> 00:06:47,143
Ni zawadi maalum zinazochomwa chini ya Kokugikan.

85
00:06:47,166 --> 00:06:50,232
Hata ikiwa baridi, bado ni tamu.

86
00:06:50,255 --> 00:06:54,224
Nitakula bila shaka!

87
00:06:54,248 --> 00:06:57,827
Je, kuna supu ya chanko?

88
00:06:57,850 --> 00:07:06,550
Ndiyo. Kwenye ukumbi mkubwa unaweza kula supu ya chanko halisi kwa shilingi mia tano tu.

89
00:07:06,573 --> 00:07:09,440
Bei rahisi sana!

90
00:07:09,463 --> 00:07:15,799
Unaweza kufurahia utamaduni wa jadi wa Kijapani na chakula kitamu kwa wakati mmoja.

91
00:07:15,822 --> 00:07:21,368
Kuna bidhaa nyingi za wabingwa maarufu wa sumo zinazouzwa.

92
00:07:21,392 --> 00:07:25,500
Ni nani mwenye nguvu zaidi sasa?

93
00:07:25,523 --> 00:07:28,259
Tafadhali niambie.

94
00:07:28,282 --> 00:07:32,453
Ni Yokozuna Hakuho.

95
00:07:32,477 --> 00:07:36,710
Anapigana na majeraha lakini anashikamana.

96
00:07:36,733 --> 00:07:40,284
Ni mtu anayefaa kuungwa mkono!

97
00:07:40,308 --> 00:07:44,503
Ninangojea wikendi kwa hamu!

98
00:07:44,526 --> 00:07:47,526
Sehemu ya 4: Mashindano ya Hamasa ya Watu Watatu Wakuu wa Kupanda Mlimani

99
00:07:47,526 --> 00:07:59,273
Mashindano ya wanaume wa kupanda mlimani hayapaswi kukosa siku hizi. Wachezaji vijana wanazidi kufanya vizuri duniani.

100
00:07:59,297 --> 00:08:06,997
Ndiyo, hasa mchezaji wa Japani, Sorato Anraku, ni mzuri sana.

101
00:08:07,020 --> 00:08:14,886
Tangu akiwa mwanafunzi wa shule ya upili, alikuwa akishinda mashindano ya watu wazima mara kwa mara.

102
00:08:14,909 --> 00:08:21,014
Mashindano ya mabingwa wake pia ni ya kiwango cha juu sana.

103
00:08:21,038 --> 00:08:27,115
Mchezaji wa Ufaransa, Mejdi Charque, pia anaitwa mzaliwa wa kipekee.

104
00:08:27,138 --> 00:08:38,297
Mejdi ana uwezo mkubwa wa kupanda miamba na mwendo wake ni wa kuvutia sana. Pia, hatuwezi kusahau mchezaji wa Korea Kusini, Lee Dohyun.

105
00:08:38,321 --> 00:08:45,491
Mchezaji I ana nguvu kubwa na huweza kupanda kuta ngumu kwa urahisi.

106
00:08:45,515 --> 00:08:52,815
Uhusiano wa ushindani kati ya hao watatu unakuwa motomoto sana kuutazama.

107
00:08:52,837 --> 00:09:00,271
Hata katika Kombe la Dunia lililopita, mpaka dakika za mwisho hatukuweza kujua nafasi zilizoshika.

108
00:09:00,294 --> 00:09:03,127
Ndiyo, ilikuwa hivyo.

109
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:08,730
Nilipata hofu wakati mchezaji Anraku alipofanya ubadilishaji wa mchezo.

110
00:09:08,754 --> 00:09:16,866
Inasemekana kwamba kwa kawaida, hao watatu ni marafiki wanaopendana sana.

111
00:09:16,889 --> 00:09:20,756
Baada ya mechi walikuwa wanacheka na kufanya hugs.

112
00:09:20,779 --> 00:09:26,368
Uhusiano wao wa kusaidiana kuboresha uwezo ni wa ajabu sana.

113
00:09:26,392 --> 00:09:33,727
Ningependa kuona tena mapambano yao ya medali katika mashindano ya kimataifa ijayo.

114
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:39,283
Siku hizi, hakuna ajabu mtu yeyote wa kushinda.

115
00:09:39,306 --> 00:09:43,901
Inaonekana kuwa umaarufu wa kupanda miamba utazidi kuongezeka.

116
00:09:43,925 --> 00:09:49,558
Sisi pia tutawashabikia kwa bidii kwenye televisheni.

117
00:09:49,581 --> 00:09:55,281
Ndiyo, nitachunguza muda wa matangazo ya moja kwa moja.

118
00:09:55,304 --> 00:09:58,304
Scene 5: Uongozi wa Ajabu wa Mori Aya / Mori Ai's Magical Lead Climbing

119
00:09:58,304 --> 00:10:03,661
Kupanda miamba kwa wanawake pia ni motomoto sana.

120
00:10:03,685 --> 00:10:08,718
Nchini Japani, kuna mtaalamu wa kupanda kwa uongozi.

121
00:10:08,741 --> 00:10:10,522
Ndio.

122
00:10:10,545 --> 00:10:16,660
Mchezo wa kupanda wa mchezaji Mori Aya unaonekana kama uchawi.

123
00:10:16,684 --> 00:10:22,317
Michezo yake ya uongozi daima huleta mshangao.

124
00:10:22,340 --> 00:10:28,973
Kuna sehemu ngumu ambapo wachezaji wengine wa kimataifa huanguka.

125
00:10:28,996 --> 00:10:30,952
Eeh.

126
00:10:30,976 --> 00:10:36,676
Mchezaji Mori ndiye pekee anayeweza kupanda kwa urahisi pale.

127
00:10:36,699 --> 00:10:43,166
Anaonekana kama anashikamana na ukuta bila graviti.

128
00:10:43,189 --> 00:10:49,826
Nguvu ya kiwiliwili na uwezo wa kustahimili ni wa kiwango cha juu sana.

129
00:10:49,849 --> 00:10:56,949
Mchezaji Mori ana urefu mdogo kidogo ukilinganisha na wengine, sivyo?

130
00:10:56,972 --> 00:10:59,283
Ndio.

131
00:10:59,306 --> 00:11:05,339
Anatumia ustadi wa hali ya juu kufidia upungufu wa urefu wake.

132
00:11:05,362 --> 00:11:13,114
Kiasi kikubwa cha mazoezi ndicho kinachosababisha mwendo wake usio na muda.

133
00:11:13,138 --> 00:11:20,696
Tofauti kati ya uso wake uliozingatia wakati wa mchezo na tabasamu baada ya mchezo ni nzuri sana.

134
00:11:20,719 --> 00:11:26,953
Kwa kawaida, yeye ni mwanafunzi wa chuo kiarifu na mnyenyekevu.

135
00:11:26,976 --> 00:11:33,876
Akim staajia ukuta, anageuka kuwa mpanda miamba bora zaidi duniani.

136
00:11:33,899 --> 00:11:39,665
Kutazama jinsi anavyopanda, unahisi kama unataka kujaribu michezo pia.

137
00:11:39,688 --> 00:11:44,122
Kuna gym ya kupanda miamba karibu na hapa.

138
00:11:44,145 --> 00:11:46,721
Tutakwenda kuijaribu?

139
00:11:46,744 --> 00:11:50,141
Je, ni salama kwa wanaoanza?

140
00:11:50,165 --> 00:11:53,332
Ninahisi hofu kidogo.

141
00:11:53,355 --> 00:11:59,192
Watafundisha kwa upole kutoka kwa njia rahisi.

142
00:11:59,215 --> 00:12:04,749
Basi, tutafanya ufuatiliaji wa majaribio mwishoni mwa wiki hii.

143
00:12:04,772 --> 00:12:09,549
Tafadhali tayarieni nguo zinazorahisisha mwendo.

144
00:12:09,572 --> 00:12:12,572
Scene 6: Mafanikio ya Wachezaji Wapya wa Japani katika MLB / Japanese MLB Players' Remarkable Performances

145
00:12:12,572 --> 00:12:18,839
Habari za ligi kuu za besiboli zinaonekana kila siku.

146
00:12:18,862 --> 00:12:25,429
Ndiyo. Mafanikio ya wachezaji wa Japani katika ligi kuu hayazimiki.

147
00:12:25,452 --> 00:12:30,806
Asubuhi hii alipiga homerun kubwa mno.

148
00:12:30,829 --> 00:12:37,026
Umbali wa mpira ulikuwa wa kushangaza sana.

149
00:12:37,049 --> 00:12:44,218
Ingawa ni mchezaji wa kweli, anafanana na mhusika wa katuni.

150
00:12:44,242 --> 00:12:51,611
Anapiga mpira kwa kasi ya kilomita 160 kwa saa na kushinda strike.

151
00:12:51,634 --> 00:12:58,268
Hakika hata Mungu wa besiboli anashangaa.

152
00:12:58,291 --> 00:13:05,233
Wafuasi wa Marekani wanashangilia sana katika uwanja.

153
00:13:05,256 --> 00:13:11,589
Inasemekana kwamba mauzo ya bidhaa zake ni ya juu zaidi katika historia ya klabu.

154
00:13:11,612 --> 00:13:18,879
Watoto wa eneo hilo wote wanavaa jezi zake.

155
00:13:18,902 --> 00:13:26,856
Si tu uwezo wake wa besiboli, bali hata tabia yake ya kukusanya takataka inapokelewa vyema.

156
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:33,712
Kwa sababu tabia yake pia ni nzuri, anapendwa duniani kote.

157
00:13:33,735 --> 00:13:41,035
Kila asubuhi nikitazama habari zake, nina nguvu kwa siku nzima.

158
00:13:41,058 --> 00:13:45,030
Hii ni kiburi cha Japani.

159
00:13:45,054 --> 00:13:49,387
Ni burudani bora kabisa.

160
00:13:49,410 --> 00:13:56,584
Napenda kuona mchezo wa moja kwa moja nchini Marekani angalau mara moja maishani.

161
00:13:56,608 --> 00:14:00,941
Uwanja wa Los Angeles, sivyo?

162
00:14:00,965 --> 00:14:04,798
Mimi pia ningependa kwenda.

163
00:14:04,821 --> 00:14:10,621
Tutafute ziara kutoka kwa kampuni ya safari?

164
00:14:10,644 --> 00:14:16,311
Inaonekana ghali, lakini thamani ya kuuona ni kubwa kabisa.

165
00:14:16,334 --> 00:14:19,367
Ndiyo, kweli.

166
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:24,733
Nitakaza kazi ili nipate fedha kwa ajili hiyo.

167
00:14:24,757 --> 00:14:31,532
Mimi pia nitatunza pesa polepole pamoja nawe.

168
00:14:31,555 --> 00:14:34,555
Sehemu ya 7: Uvutio wa Mpira wa Kikazi wa Japani

169
00:14:34,555 --> 00:14:40,313
Umewahi kwenda kuuona mpira wa kikazi wa Japani?

170
00:14:40,337 --> 00:14:45,084
Ndiyo, nimekwenda mara kadhaa.

171
00:14:45,108 --> 00:14:49,541
Napenda sana hali ya uwanjani.

172
00:14:49,564 --> 00:14:56,731
Utamaduni wa msaada wa Japani ni tofauti kabisa na michezo ya mpira wa kikazi ya nje.

173
00:14:56,754 --> 00:15:04,120
Ndiyo. Naamini wageni wote wanashangaa wakati wa kwanza wa kwenda.

174
00:15:04,143 --> 00:15:10,612
Watu wa kikundi cha msaada kwenye stendi ya kulia wanapiga tarumbeta.

175
00:15:10,636 --> 00:15:17,809
Ndiyo. Kisha watazamaji wote wanaimba kwa sauti kubwa pamoja nao.

176
00:15:17,833 --> 00:15:24,375
Ni nini hasa kuhusu nyimbo za msaada zinazotofautiana kwa kila mchezaji?

177
00:15:24,399 --> 00:15:30,865
Ni kizuri sana kusikia wimbo wako ukicheza wakati wa kuingia kwenye besi.

178
00:15:30,888 --> 00:15:37,522
Kabla ya mchezo wa raundi ya saba, kuna tukio maalum.

179
00:15:37,545 --> 00:15:44,487
Wanapiga wimbo wa klabu na kurusha baluni rangi za kuvutia.

180
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:47,343
Ndio.

181
00:15:47,366 --> 00:15:52,835
Mandhari ya baluni zinazojaza anga ni ya kuvutia sana.

182
00:15:52,858 --> 00:16:00,001
Unapoona hiyo, unahisi kama uwanja wote umekuwa eneo la sherehe.

183
00:16:00,025 --> 00:16:07,142
Si mchezo pekee, lakini pia vyakula vya uwanjani ni furaha mojawapo.

184
00:16:07,165 --> 00:16:13,485
Kuna chakula cha mikeka na tamu nyingi zilizoundwa na wachezaji.

185
00:16:13,508 --> 00:16:20,541
Kama ni uwanja wa ndani, hata kukiwa na mvua, mchezo hautaondolewa, hivyo ni salama.

186
00:16:20,564 --> 00:16:26,464
Bia baridi inayouzwa na dada wa kuuza pia ni bora kabisa.

187
00:16:26,487 --> 00:16:32,754
Siku hizi, tutualike marafiki wengi na kwenda pamoja, sivyo?

188
00:16:32,777 --> 00:16:36,844
Ni furaha zaidi iwapo tutakuwa na sherehe kubwa.

189
00:16:36,867 --> 00:16:40,900
Tutafute mchezo wa mwezi ujao.

190
00:16:40,923 --> 00:16:47,823
Kama ni mchezo wa Jumanne usiku, tutaweza kwenda baada ya kazi.

191
00:16:47,846 --> 00:16:50,113
Sawa kabisa.

192
00:16:50,136 --> 00:16:54,727
Tufanye iwe usiku wa Ijumaa wa premium.

193
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:57,750
Sehemu ya 8: Mabadiliko ya Mbinu za Timu ya Taifa ya Japani ya Mpira wa Vole

194
00:16:57,750 --> 00:17:05,736
Hivi majuzi, timu ya taifa ya wanaume ya mpira wa vole ya Japani imekuwa nguvu sana.

195
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:12,526
Hata katika mashindano ya dunia, wanashinda nchi zenye nguvu moja baada ya nyingine.

196
00:17:12,549 --> 00:17:19,616
Ikilinganishwa na mpira wa vole wa zamani, mbinu zimeendelea sana.

197
00:17:19,639 --> 00:17:27,276
Ndiyo. Mbinu za mashambulizi zina kasi isiyoweza kusadikiwa.

198
00:17:27,299 --> 00:17:34,204
Mchezaji wa kuweka mpira anafanya kazi vizuri sana na kudanganya bloku ya adui.

199
00:17:34,228 --> 00:17:40,505
Shambulio la nyuma pia lina nguvu sana.

200
00:17:40,528 --> 00:17:47,086
Uwezo wa mchezaji wa libero katika kupokea pia ni wa kiwango cha juu duniani.

201
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:54,468
Ni ajabu jinsi wanavyoweza kuzuia spiki yoyote isiangukie sakafuni.

202
00:17:54,492 --> 00:18:00,034
Mwonekano wa wachezaji pia ni wa kuvutia na una umaarufu mkubwa.

203
00:18:00,058 --> 00:18:06,411
Uwanjani, kuna mashabiki wengi sana.

204
00:18:06,434 --> 00:18:13,829
Lakini nadhani sababu ya umaarufu ni uwezo wao wa hali ya juu.

205
00:18:13,852 --> 00:18:17,119
Nakubaliana nawe.

206
00:18:17,142 --> 00:18:22,889
Wachezaji wote wanapiga mpira kwa bidii kwa ajili ya timu.

207
00:18:22,912 --> 00:18:30,079
Kwa kuwa mpira wa vole ni mchezo usio wa kushika mpira, sivyo?

208
00:18:30,102 --> 00:18:37,135
Ndiyo. Ndiyo maana imani kati ya wenzako ni muhimu zaidi.

209
00:18:37,158 --> 00:18:45,258
Unapoangalia mchezo, moyo wako hupashwa moto na nguvu zaidi katika msaada.

210
00:18:45,281 --> 00:18:52,448
Katika Olimpiki ijayo, kuna matarajio makubwa ya kupata medali.

211
00:18:52,471 --> 00:18:58,337
Napenda kuona kwa macho yangu mabadiliko ya historia yanapotokea.

212
00:18:58,360 --> 00:19:04,352
Usiku huu kuna mchezo wa moja kwa moja katika televisheni.

213
00:19:04,376 --> 00:19:11,126
Lazima nirudi nyumbani haraka na kusubiri mbele ya televisheni.

214
00:19:11,149 --> 00:19:16,249
Nitununulie chakula cha kando, nitaichezea pia.

215
00:19:16,272 --> 00:19:19,272
Sehemu ya 9: Uvutio wa Kuangalia Mchezo wa B.League

216
00:19:19,272 --> 00:19:26,739
Wikendi iliyopita, niliangalia mchezo wa B.League kwa mara ya kwanza.

217
00:19:26,762 --> 00:19:30,836
Ni mpira wa kikapu wa kulipwa nchini Japani.

218
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:33,769
Ulikuwa unaonaje?

219
00:19:33,792 --> 00:19:40,825
Mazoezi ndani ya ukumbi wa michezo yalikuwa kama vilabu.

220
00:19:40,848 --> 00:19:46,956
Kuna muziki wa sauti kubwa na maonyesho ya taa ya kuvutia, sivyo?

221
00:19:46,979 --> 00:19:49,513
Ndio.

222
00:19:49,536 --> 00:19:55,769
Hata kabla ya mchezo kuanza, DJ alikuwa akihamasisha uwanja.

223
00:19:55,792 --> 00:20:02,059
Ni nafasi ambayo hata wasiofahamu mpira wa kikapu wanaweza kufurahia.

224
00:20:02,082 --> 00:20:10,415
Ndiyo, mchezo ulipoanza, nikaishia kushangaa na kasi yake.

225
00:20:10,438 --> 00:20:16,371
Uwanja ni mdogo, hivyo umbali na wachezaji ni fupi sana.

226
00:20:16,394 --> 00:20:23,828
Nilipoona dunk shot mbele yangu, nililia kwa sauti kubwa.

227
00:20:23,851 --> 00:20:28,717
Ulikuwa na nguvu kiasi cha kuonekana kama lengo lingebomoka.

228
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:30,974
Ndio.

229
00:20:30,997 --> 00:20:37,032
Pia, mchezo ulikuwa una mabadiliko hadi mwisho.

230
00:20:37,055 --> 00:20:43,522
Kama mchezo wa kugeuza ushindi katika sekunde za mwisho, ndio ladha ya mpira wa kikapu.

231
00:20:43,545 --> 00:20:47,020
Kweli kabisa.

232
00:20:47,044 --> 00:20:52,917
Goli la pointi tatu liliingia wakati sekunde tatu zilikuwa zimesalia.

233
00:20:52,940 --> 00:20:56,173
Ushindi wa ajabu!

234
00:20:56,196 --> 00:21:00,629
Hamasa ya watazamaji ilikuwa inafika.

235
00:21:00,652 --> 00:21:07,848
Uwanja wote ulikuwa unatawanyika kwa sauti ya furaha, na nilipelekea ngozi yangu kusimama.

236
00:21:07,871 --> 00:21:12,052
Bei ya tiketi ilikuwa kiasi gani?

237
00:21:12,076 --> 00:21:18,624
Kwa kiti cha kawaida, mtu mzima anaweza kununua kwa takribani yenye Shilingi elfu tatu.

238
00:21:18,647 --> 00:21:24,881
Kwa bei hiyo na uzoefu huo, thamani ya pesa ni bora kabisa.

239
00:21:24,904 --> 00:21:29,804
Je, tutaenda pamoja kuuangalia mchezo mwingine?

240
00:21:29,827 --> 00:21:32,860
Utaipenda bila shaka.

241
00:21:32,883 --> 00:21:36,716
Tafadhali niongoze.

242
00:21:36,739 --> 00:21:40,337
Ninataka kununua vifaa vya msaada pia.

243
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:46,060
Tujifunike na tisheti za rangi za timu na kutoa kelele tena.

244
00:21:46,083 --> 00:21:49,083
Sehemu ya 10: Mapigano ya Kasi ya Mpira wa Meza

245
00:21:49,083 --> 00:21:55,617
Niliona fainali ya mashindano ya kimataifa ya mpira wa meza kwenye televisheni.

246
00:21:55,640 --> 00:22:00,806
Ilikuwa mapigano ya moto kati ya Japani na Uchina.

247
00:22:00,829 --> 00:22:03,529
Uliuona?

248
00:22:03,552 --> 00:22:05,868
Ndio.

249
00:22:05,892 --> 00:22:12,287
Kasi ya rally ilikuwa haraka mno hata sikupiga bongo.

250
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:18,943
Wanacheza mpira katika sehemu ya sekonde chache.

251
00:22:18,966 --> 00:22:25,600
Uwezo wa kuona kwa haraka na mrejesho wa haraka unahisi kama si wa kibinadamu.

252
00:22:25,623 --> 00:22:34,689
Uchina, mabingwa wasio na mpinzani, ni ngumu mno kuvunja ukuta wao.

253
00:22:34,712 --> 00:22:41,046
Walikuwa na aina nyingi za mzunguko na hawakufanya makosa yoyote.

254
00:22:41,069 --> 00:22:49,010
Lakini, wachezaji wadogo wa Japani hawakukata tamaa hadi mwisho.

255
00:22:49,034 --> 00:22:57,107
Ndiyo. Nililia nilipoona wao kuchukua seti moja kutoka kwa bingwa wa Uchina.

256
00:22:57,130 --> 00:23:04,163
Sauti kubwa ya kila wakati wa kupata pointi ilionyesha nguvu zao.

257
00:23:04,186 --> 00:23:07,920
Kweli kabisa.

258
00:23:07,943 --> 00:23:13,380
Hamasa yao ilitoka kwenye skrini.

259
00:23:13,403 --> 00:23:20,270
Zamani ilikuwa inasemekana kuwa ni mchezo wa kawaida, lakini sasa si tena.

260
00:23:20,293 --> 00:23:27,632
Sasa ni mmoja wa michezo maarufu na inayovutia zaidi nchini Japani.

261
00:23:27,655 --> 00:23:33,968
Inasemekana idadi ya watoto wanaocheza inazidi kuongezeka.

262
00:23:33,991 --> 00:23:40,858
Ni furaha kuona wabingwa wa baadaye wanavyokua sasa.

263
00:23:40,881 --> 00:23:48,351
Nilipoangalia mchezo, nilitamani kucheza mpira wa meza wa maji moto.

264
00:23:48,374 --> 00:23:54,407
Lazima tuanze mazoezi kwa kushika raketi vizuri kwanza.

265
00:23:54,430 --> 00:24:01,428
Kwenye onsen, hata kama huchezi vizuri, unaweza kucheza meza kwa furaha na tabasamu.

266
00:24:01,451 --> 00:24:07,685
Sawa, tuta mpango wa safari ya onsen ili kupumzika na kufurahia wakati huu.

267
00:24:07,708 --> 00:24:14,141
Nitatafuta haraka kwa mtandao mahoteli yenye meza ya tenisi ya meza.